from\": 2925, \"to\": 2939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgium gets back on the front to control the gap, but with no representation in the front group and only a fatigued Tiesj Benoot left to set the pace, this is a precarious situation for the race's dominant team.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3016, \"end\": 3023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999996312054235, \"rank\": 3.687948129934768e-07, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiesj_Benoot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tiesj Benoot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiesj_Benoot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiesj_Benoot\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"no representation\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"the front group\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"a precarious situation\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"the race's dominant team\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"46km:When they hit the cobbled climb of Butte Montmartre, with Healy still solo, the peloton 40 seconds behind the strong chase group, and Belgium having no domestiques left to reel in them, Mathieu van der Poel attacks and is immediately followed by Wout Van Aert and a small group of elite riders who ride clear.\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3278, \"end\": 3288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.414312401541311e-21, \"text\": \"Montmartre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\"}, {\"begin\": 3423, \"end\": 3443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathieu van der Poel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\"}, {\"begin\": 3423, \"end\": 3443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathieu van der Poel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\"}, {\"begin\": 3483, \"end\": 3496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wout Van Aert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cobbled climb\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3268}, {\"ngram\": \"Healy\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"the strong chase group\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3365}, {\"ngram\": \"no domestiques\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3400}, {\"ngram\": \"a small group\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"elite riders\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"38.6km:This escape group, which is mainly being driven by Van der Poel and Jorgenson, is eventually reeled in by Mads Pedersen, who missed it due to an ill-timed flat, with the peloton following closely behind.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3663, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9973584045699821, \"rank\": 0.002648129758357