ine, with Van der Poel sitting near the front marking Van Aert, Remco Evenepoel sees the perfect opportunity and launches a perfectly timed attack.\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 4070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3987, \"end\": 4002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the groups\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Aert\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect opportunity\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4031}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfectly timed attack\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"38km:Unlike his previous attacks, Evenepoel's move immediately opens up significant daylight due to the group being gassed from the just-completed chase.\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his previous attacks\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel's move\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"significant daylight\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4181}, {\"ngram\": \"the just-completed chase\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel is able to quickly bridge up to the chase group, which is now just 11 seconds ahead, while Healy is still impressively alone on the front.\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"the chase group\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4283}, {\"ngram\": \"Healy\", \"from\": 4327, \"to\": 4332}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"27.8km:On the second pass of Butte Montmartre, with Evenepoel ripping through the front groups and the peloton now 45 seconds behind him, Van der Poel attacks again.\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4413, \"end\": 4423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.414312401541311e-21, \"text\": \"Montmartre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second pass\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4403}, {\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4439}, {\"ngram\": \"the front groups\", \"from\": 4456, \"to\": 4472}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he is again closely marked by Van Aert, who refuses to pull through due to his 'teammate' being up the road.\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Aert\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4591}, {\"ngram\": \"his 'teammate\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 4652, \"to\": 4660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At this point, with Evenepoel off the front, Van der Poel unable to shake Van Aert, and Van Aert showing he is here to support his national team, the race is essentially over.\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4675}, {\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4719}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Aert\", \"from\": 4736, \"to\": 4744}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Aert\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4758}, {\"ngram\": \"his national team\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"21.5km:Up front, after hurricane Evenepoel has ripped through the groups, the only rider remaining on his wheel is Madouas.\", \"from\": 4841, \"to\": 4964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4956, \"end\": 4963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madouas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hurricane Evenepoel\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"the groups\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4913}, {\"ngram\": \"the only rider\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4929}, {\"ngram\": \"his wheel\", \"from\": 4943, \"to\": 4952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Madouas is sitting behind Evenepoel, the difference in the two riders' aerodynamic positions means that Madouas is struggling to get a draft.\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 5118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4977, \"end\": 4984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madouas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\"}, {\"begin\": 5081, \"end\": 5088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madouas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5012}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5028}, {\"ngram\": \"the two riders' aerodynamic positions\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5069}, {\"ngram\": \"a draft\", \"from\": 5110, \"to\": 5117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With 44 seconds on the Van der Poel peloton and knowing he can drop Madouas at will, Evenepoel has settled into a relatively controlled pace.\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5260, \"entities\": [{\"begin